<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Add a Zend_Controller_Action::_setParam() method to allow modifying request parameters (reported by Sylvain Philip in fw-general).</p>

<p>Usage:</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
$this-&gt;_setParam($name, $value)
</code></pre>

<p>Implementation:
```
protected function _setParam($name, $value)
{
    $this-&gt;getRequest()-&gt;setParam($name, $value);
    return $this;
}</p>

